## Gap Analysis: Your Sub-Phases Are Incomplete

Your sub-phases 2.4 and 2.5 cover **generic habit completion** (mark as done/missed) and **streaks/freezes/dashboard** — but they **completely miss** making `numeric`, `timer`, and `checklist` types functional. Here's what's missing:

| Type | Your sub-phases cover this? | What's actually needed |
|---|---|---|
| **boolean** | ✅ Yes — `status: completed` in `habit_logs` | Nothing extra |
| **numeric** | ❌ No | `habit_logs.value` column + "I did 5 out of 8" input UI |
| **timer** | ❌ No | `habit_logs.duration_seconds` column + stopwatch UI component |
| **checklist** | ❌ No | `habit_checklist_items` table + draggable checklist UI |

Without addressing these, `numeric`/`timer`/`checklist` remain empty shells — users pay to unlock them but get zero functionality beyond a label.

---

## Complete Phased Plan (Single Source of Truth)


### PHASE 5: Frontend — Type-Specific Form UI

**Goal:** Habit form shows relevant fields for each type.

| Build | Details |
|---|---|
| Update `HabitFormModal` | `numeric` → target + unit (already done). `timer` → default duration input. `checklist` → add/remove/sort checklist items |
| Update `habit.ts` types | Add `checklist_items` to `Habit`, add log types |
| Update `HabitPayload` | Add `checklist_items` array |

**Files to modify:**
- `src/components/user/habits/HabitFormModal.tsx`
- `src/types/habit.ts`

---

### PHASE 6: Frontend — Logging UI (The Core)

**Goal:** Users can actually complete their habits from the habits page.

| Build | Details |
|---|---|
| `useHabitLogs` hook | `logHabit`, `updateLog`, `deleteLog` mutations + today's logs query |
| `habitLogService` | API calls for log CRUD |
| Update `HabitCard` | `boolean` → checkbox. `numeric` → number input with progress. `timer` → start/stop/reset stopwatch. `checklist` → checkable sub-items |
| `TimerWidget` component | Stopwatch with start/pause/reset, returns seconds on save |
| `ChecklistLog` component | Renders checklist items with checkboxes for today |
| `NumericLog` component | Number input + "out of {target} {unit}" label |
| Update `HabitsPage` | Fetch today's logs, pass to `HabitGrid` → `HabitCard` |
| Optimistic updates | Checkbox/input updates immediately, reverts on API error |

**Files to create/modify:**
- `src/services/user/habitLogService.ts` (new)
- `src/hooks/user/useHabitLogs.ts` (new)
- `src/components/user/habits/TimerWidget.tsx` (new)
- `src/components/user/habits/ChecklistLog.tsx` (new)
- `src/components/user/habits/NumericLog.tsx` (new)
- Modify: `src/components/user/habits/HabitCard.tsx`
- Modify: `src/components/user/habits/HabitGrid.tsx`
- Modify: `src/pages/user/HabitsPage.tsx`
- `src/types/habit.ts`

---

### PHASE 7: Frontend — Streaks, Freezes & Dashboard

**Goal:** Visual streak display, freeze functionality, dashboard page.

| Build | Details |
|---|---|
| `useStreaks` hook | Streak data query |
| `useStreakFreezes` hook | Apply freeze mutation with quota check |
| `StreakBadge` component | 🔥 12 days |
| `FreezeButton` component | Checks quota, shows lock if limit reached |
| Update `HabitCard` | Show streak badge + freeze button for missed days |
| `DashboardPage` | Today's progress, completion ring, quota indicators |
| `QuotaIndicator` component | Dynamic progress bar from quota API |
| `QuotaBanner` component | 80% threshold upsell banner |

**Files to create/modify:**
- `src/hooks/user/useStreaks.ts` (new)
- `src/hooks/user/useStreakFreezes.ts` (new)
- `src/services/user/streakService.ts` (new)
